rComments: Best class I had all year
We read articles on paleogenomics in the course. The research we discussed was very interesting.
This online class was the hardest ever! It is also intense because it is four credit hours.

Dr. Malhi is extremely intelligent and interesting to listen to. But he is very monotone and it's so hard to stay attentive for an hour and a half. The quizzes had difficult questions that were unfairly worded and he would not give credit for them.
